Author: KomodoWorld#8282
Content: https://www.stevens.edu/news/how-social-medias-powerful-silent-majority-moves-bitcoin-prices

Author: KomodoWorld#8282
Content:
"Very active users' comments and tweets, Mai's team found, did not move Bitcoin's price much at all. However, the "silent majority" ‚Äî infrequent Twitter and Bitcointalk users who took the time to comment on the cryptocurrency's prospects ‚Äî moved prices more, as much as ten times more, when they posted positive comments."

"This was a big finding, and it does seem to prove that people are trusting the silent majority much more, perhaps because they do not seem to have an agenda," says Mai.
